    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape, super reliable, and still looks great parked in the driveway. It has been well-loved and is totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner. If you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you! Let's get you behind the wheel!",
